{"tid":652874,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[不服來辯]香港冇任何一間食店屈機得過吉野家","createTime":"2018-05-04T07:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T06:48:38.000Z","uid":137719,"like":405,"dislike":121,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"63f6cf95baf2778bb1f5e7ebf8cbe3a2cc2c2af9","tid":652874,"uid":137719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T07:59:40.000Z","msg":"呢排飲食台見到咁多打手 不停吹奏大快活 大家樂呢類垃圾食物<br />\n連改變左成個人生都UP得出口 我真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果雞胸飯可以改變成個人生 我夠膽講 吉野家牛肉飯絕對可以改變香港飲食業未來<br />\n點樣睇一間食店係咪好食店 就要由最基本既食物質素入手 <br />\n野好唔好食 份量同味道穩唔穩定都好重要 <br />\n吉野家最出名既牛飯相信大家都食過<br />\n牛肉飯入面每一塊牛肉都經過日本豉油幾千秒長時間既浸淫<br />\n牛肉唔單止上到色 亦都吸收晒吉野家秘製醬汁既味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食落去充滿油香 肥而不膩 再加埋沾上少量牛汁既珍珠米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/155501_88ee3aeaaa59c99f6bcacfd743ee764e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F155501_88ee3aeaaa59c99f6bcacfd743ee764e.jpg&h=cd3fd369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此美食絕對係只應天上有 人間能得幾回嚐 但係加阿叔同你講 簡簡單單去吉野家就食到<br />\n至於吉野家既雞飯 絕對可以屌打個乜春南瓜汁雞胸飯<br />\n唔好話雞飯 一舊雞最緊要既靈魂係咩? 冇錯 就係雞皮<br />\n冇左雞皮既雞就好似條女冇左對波一樣 食之無味棄之可惜<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/155004_56ba94f3ed3d8dfb1ef8ef796be348da.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F155004_56ba94f3ed3d8dfb1ef8ef796be348da.gif&h=63278fda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔通好似傻校長咁 食雞唔食雞皮 食橙食埋橙皮咩<br />\n所以話個乜春南瓜汁雞胸飯連食既價值都冇<br />\n吉野家雞飯絕對&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;乜春南瓜汁雞胸飯<br />\n除左食物質素之外 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">價錢都好撚重要 係呢方面 吉野家完勝其他99.9999%既食店</span></span><br />\n下午茶細牛細雞都係都係廿幾 凍飲加兩蚊 想食菜可以叫 野菜雞/牛 <br />\n想食豪D可以叫玉子雞/牛 全部都係廿零蚊<br />\n所以我依加係度正式宣佈 吉野家係最尾機既食店 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不服來辯<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"8e6a790de4f7010bdb6634a3547fc6538b41c91c","tid":652874,"uid":171124,"like":39,"dislike":132,"score":-93,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:00:49.000Z","msg":"大快活一個雞排搞撚掂你"},{"pid":"a15a948d9070d08f21fe9c3d7c7df54d505dabfc","tid":652874,"uid":90726,"like":47,"dislike":5,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:02:44.000Z","msg":"有撚豉油咩on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1455f0a41b446aa9b7c005b43ba61152bed1652","tid":652874,"uid":7954,"like":139,"dislike":0,"score":139,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:03:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79e6812fe004c3ea1a260ad728352324cdc80f01","tid":652874,"uid":137719,"like":12,"dislike":15,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"8e6a790de4f7010bdb6634a3547fc6538b41c91c","tid":652874,"uid":171124,"like":39,"dislike":132,"score":-93,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:00:49.000Z","msg":"大快活一個雞排搞撚掂你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:06:13.000Z","msg":"笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5fee3ab52ca4c1d3c4c92da72878599484e861","tid":652874,"uid":129013,"like":54,"dislike":3,"score":51,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:07:22.000Z","msg":"食牛飯一定要叫個牛汁，但我唔係倒落d飯度，我會用嚟點牛肉食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641d15f3b054bfdbea02b7a7835afa4e22bff695","tid":652874,"uid":4064,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"fc5fee3ab52ca4c1d3c4c92da72878599484e861","tid":652874,"uid":129013,"like":54,"dislike":3,"score":51,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:07:22.000Z","msg":"食牛飯一定要叫個牛汁，但我唔係倒落d飯度，我會用嚟點牛肉食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/to